{"tid":961340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【涉毒入獄中】AV女優麻生希被捕片段曝光","createTime":"2018-12-30T05:00:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-30T05:07:56.000Z","uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bb00307bc24895c3934b115b5093e9314e984d1e","tid":961340,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T05:00:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181230/photo/bkn-20181230110936767-1230_00862_001_01p.jpg?20181230121333\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20181230%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181230110936767-1230_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20181230121333&h=af17670d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181230/photo/bkn-20181230110936767-1230_00862_001_03b.jpg?20181230121333\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20181230%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181230110936767-1230_00862_001_03b.jpg%3F20181230121333&h=9ac8fea7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n墮落<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n曾演出港產片《豪情3D》床戰杜汶澤的33歲日本AV女優麻生希（原名島崎彩），今年2月再度爆出涉毒，警方在她與男友高畑愛平位於東京目黑區的寓所搜出興奮劑、大麻等毒品。拘留期間，她又被爆未婚懷孕，並因吸毒而令BB早產夭折。最終，麻生希被判入獄1年8個月，守行為4個月。<br />\n<br />\n昨日，有日本電視台公開麻生希當日被捕片段。當日，她與一名男子在家中吸毒。片中麻生希剷了Skinhead頭，似是為逃避警方追查，與以往留長髮、被封「AV林志玲」的她判若兩人。警員以其真名問她是否島崎彩本人，麻生希大方答：「係」。據知麻生希因為生計，亦有從事買賣毒品活動。麻生希於前年7月曾因傳持有毒品被捕，當地毒品調查部門認為她有再犯傾向，因此數月前已向她作出調查。"},{"pid":"c8736c58f8df65bd7a7ac45e7c3edb13801b244d","tid":961340,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T05:04:38.000Z","msg":"差咁遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fcda4d1d4009a75dfb99af15f939ca37a433cc5","tid":961340,"uid":7206,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T05:06:57.000Z","msg":"av林志玲唔係波多野咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5aa967a584203b7e0de42f6edd84e9e0d0365b2","tid":961340,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T05:07:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}